OL,3,C'I was tricked into breaking the law':
OL,4,CMan lured into being a 'money mule'
OL,6,FDarren, from Lampeter, told ITV Wales'
OL,7,FY Byd ar Bedwar that he became
OL,8,Finvolved last year, but was unaware
OL,9,Fthat what seemed a simple way to make
OL,10,Fmoney, was actually a crime.
OL,12,FAt the time, he was part of groups on
OL,13,Fsocial media advertising ways to make
OL,14,Fmoney, and although not all of these
OL,15,Fwere scams, his membership made him an
OL,16,Feasy target for criminals.
