OL,3,C'I was tricked into breaking the law':
OL,4,CMan lured into being a 'money mule'
OL,6,FHis girlfriend was also taking part in
OL,7,Fsimilar transfers, and often used his
OL,8,Faccounts to move funds. They both felt
OL,9,Funder pressure to take part, but also
OL,10,Fbelieved it was a legitimate scheme at
OL,11,Fthe time.
OL,13,FDarren says, "my partner would send
OL,14,Fmoney to my account, then to her
OL,15,Faccount, and onwards to other people".
OL,17,F"I wasn't bothered at the time, but
OL,18,Fthinking about it now makes me feel
OL,19,Fsick. It's just dirty money".
