OL,6,FIndividuals identified as having
OL,7,Fallowed their accounts to be used in
OL,8,Fthis way may receive a CIFAS fraud
OL,9,Fmarker.
OL,11,FCIFAS is the main service for
OL,12,Fpreventing financial fraud in the
OL,13,FUnited Kingdom. If a person has a
OL,14,FCIFAS marker by their name, it informs
OL,15,Fall banks that they have been involved
OL,16,Fin fraud, making it more difficult to
OL,17,Fopen accounts and get loans for up to
OL,18,Fsix years.
