OL,4,CMan lured into being a 'money mule'
OL,6,FFfion Edwards, an Economic Crime
OL,7,FOfficer at Starling Bank, says banks
OL,8,Fwill often close accounts where they
OL,9,Fbelieve the customer has taken part in
OL,10,Fmoney muling.
OL,12,FShe says individuals that are placed
OL,13,Fon industry databases such as CIFAS
OL,14,Fcan face long-term consequences
OL,15,Faffecting "mortgages, credit cards,
OL,16,Fand financial freedom".
