OL,3,C'I was tricked into breaking the law':
OL,4,CMan lured into being a 'money mule'
OL,6,FAccording to Crimestoppers, 3 in every
OL,7,F5 students in Wales have been
OL,8,Fapproached with offers to money mule.
OL,9,FFfion says criminals deliberately
OL,10,Fdeliberately target people they
OL,11,Fbelieve they can exploit.
OL,13,F"Often they target people between the
OL,14,Fages of 18-30 who need money,
OL,15,Fvulnerable people, people with a lack
OL,16,Fof financial understanding, and people
OL,17,Fwho don't understand the criminal
OL,18,Frepercussions".
