OL,6,FWales is a hotspot for fraud.
OL,7,FAccording to research by The Co-
OL,8,Foperative Bank, North Wales is the
OL,9,Fworst in the UK, with 3,005 reports of
OL,10,Ffraud in the year ending November 2024
OL,11,F(equating to 43 cases per 1,000
OL,12,Fresidents). This totals a loss of #10
OL,13,Fmillion.
