OL,3,C'I was tricked into breaking the law':
OL,4,CMan lured into being a 'money mule'
OL,6,FNorth Wales Police has a dedicated
OL,7,Ffinancial crime unit to try and tackle
OL,8,Fthis issue. Detective Inspector Iolo
OL,9,FEdwards says they deal with money
OL,10,Fmuling related cases on a daily basis.
OL,12,FHe says officers assess whether an
OL,13,Findividual is a victim before taking
OL,14,Ffurther action, and many cases result
OL,15,Fin warnings such as a cease and
OL,16,Fdesist. But he stresses that the most
OL,17,Fserious offences can lead to
OL,18,Fsignificant consequences.
OL,20,F"You could go to prison for up to 14
OL,21,Fyears".
