OL,3,C'I was tricked into breaking the law':
OL,4,CMan lured into being a 'money mule'
OL,6,F"I'm sure that the people who accept
OL,7,Fthese offers online don't think about
OL,8,Fthe consequences, but they have to
OL,9,Fstart thinking about it as a door to
OL,10,Fcourt."
OL,12,FHe warns that "people have to realise
OL,13,Fthat others will try to scam them. And
OL,14,Fat the end of the day, money muling is
OL,15,Fa crime."
OL,17,FFor Darren, he says that he has
OL,18,Fstopped participating in this, and is
OL,19,Fcalling for more awareness about
OL,20,Fsimilar scams.
